title: Api

title: Merchant items
body:
Pull request for Merchant Items Collection, user stories 7-13. 

Added  features: Merchant Items Show Page,  Merchant Item Update, Merchant Item Disable/Enable, Merchant Items Grouped by Status, Merchant Item Create, Merchant Items Index: 5 most popular items, Merchant Items Index: Top Item's Best Day. 

All features and models are tested and passing. 

Refactoring opportunities: Make test more robust by fully covering all edge cases and sad paths. Clean up and better organize test data in spec files. Add styling to views.
